- Changed `alias mkvenv='python3 -m venv venv'` to `alias mkvenv='uv venv'`
- Changed `alias venv='source venv/bin/activate'` to `alias venv='source .venv/bin/activate'`
- Changed `alias mysql='mysql --default-character-set=utf8mb4 -u root -p'` to `alias mysql='mycli -u root'`
- Added `alias myclirc='vim ~/.myclirc'`
- Added `envpy()` function for quick Python environment creation

**New Function - envpy():**
```bash
envpy() {
    local name="${1:-venv}"
    if [ -d "$name" ]; then
        echo "venv '$name' already exists"
        return 1
    fi
    uv venv "$name"
    source "$name/bin/activate"
    uv pip install pytest ruff mypy
}
```

