### 5. install
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
**Changes:**
- Improved shell detection with proper error handling
- Added check for zsh availability before changing shell

**Old Code:**
```bash
[ "$SHELL" != "/bin/zsh" ] && chsh -s $(which zsh)
```

**New Code:**
```bash
if [ "$SHELL" != "/bin/zsh" ]; then
    if command -v zsh >/dev/null 2>&1; then
        chsh -s "$(command -v zsh)" || echo "Warning: Unable to change login shell automatically."
    else
        echo "Skipping login shell change because zsh is not installed."
    fi
fi
```

